var book = {
	"name": "1 Corinthians",
	"numChapters": 16,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, called to be an apostle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28365A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28365A\"></sup> of Christ Jesus by the will of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28365B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28365B\"></sup> and our brother Sosthenes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28365C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28365C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To the church of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28366D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28366D\"></sup> in Corinth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28366E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28366E\"></sup> to those sanctified in Christ Jesus and called<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28366F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28366F\"></sup> to be his holy people, together with all those everywhere who call on the name<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28366G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28366G\"></sup> of our Lord Jesus Christ—their Lord and ours:",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Grace and peace to you from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28367H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28367H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I always thank my God for you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28368I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28368I\"></sup> because of his grace given you in Christ Jesus.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For in him you have been enriched<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28369J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28369J\"></sup> in every way—with all kinds of speech and with all knowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28369K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28369K\"></sup>—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>God thus confirming our testimony<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28370L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28370L\"></sup> about Christ among you.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore you do not lack any spiritual gift<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28371M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28371M\"></sup> as you eagerly wait for our Lord Jesus Christ to be revealed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28371N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28371N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He will also keep you firm to the end, so that you will be blameless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28372O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28372O\"></sup> on the day of our Lord Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28372P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28372P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>God is faithful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28373Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28373Q\"></sup> who has called you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28373R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28373R\"></sup> into fellowship with his Son, Jesus Christ our Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28373S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28373S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I appeal to you, brothers and sisters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28374T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28374T\"></sup> in the name of our Lord Jesus Christ, that all of you agree with one another in what you say and that there be no divisions among you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28374U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28374U\"></sup> but that you be perfectly united<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28374V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28374V\"></sup> in mind and thought.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>My brothers and sisters, some from Chloe’s household<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28375W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28375W\"></sup> have informed me that there are quarrels among you.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>What I mean is this: One of you says, “I follow Paul”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28376X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28376X\"></sup> another, “I follow Apollos”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28376Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28376Y\"></sup> another, “I follow Cephas”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28376Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28376Z\"></sup> still another, “I follow Christ.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Is Christ divided? Was Paul crucified for you? Were you baptized in the name of Paul?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28377AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28377AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I thank God that I did not baptize any of you except Crispus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28378AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28378AB\"></sup> and Gaius,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28378AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28378AC\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>so no one can say that you were baptized in my name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>(Yes, I also baptized the household<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28380AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28380AD\"></sup> of Stephanas;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28380AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28380AE\"></sup> beyond that, I don’t remember if I baptized anyone else.)",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For Christ did not send me to baptize,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28381AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28381AF\"></sup> but to preach the gospel—not with wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28381AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28381AG\"></sup> and eloquence, lest the cross of Christ be emptied of its power.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For the message of the cross is foolishness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28382AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28382AH\"></sup> to those who are perishing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28382AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28382AI\"></sup> but to us who are being saved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28382AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28382AJ\"></sup> it is the power of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28382AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28382AK\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For it is written:“I will destroy the wisdom of the wise;the intelligence of the intelligent I will frustrate.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28383AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28383AL\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Where is the wise person?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28384AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28384AM\"></sup> Where is the teacher of the law? Where is the philosopher of this age?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28384AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28384AN\"></sup> Has not God made foolish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28384AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28384AO\"></sup> the wisdom of the world?",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For since in the wisdom of God the world<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28385AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28385AP\"></sup> through its wisdom did not know him, God was pleased through the foolishness of what was preached to save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28385AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28385AQ\"></sup> those who believe.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28385AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28385AR\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Jews demand signs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28386AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28386AS\"></sup> and Greeks look for wisdom,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>but we preach Christ crucified:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28387AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28387AT\"></sup> a stumbling block<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28387AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28387AU\"></sup> to Jews and foolishness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28387AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28387AV\"></sup> to Gentiles,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>but to those whom God has called,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28388AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28388AW\"></sup> both Jews and Greeks, Christ the power of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28388AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28388AX\"></sup> and the wisdom of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28388AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28388AY\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For the foolishness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28389AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28389AZ\"></sup> of God is wiser than human wisdom, and the weakness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28389BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28389BA\"></sup> of God is stronger than human strength.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Brothers and sisters, think of what you were when you were called.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28390BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28390BB\"></sup> Not many of you were wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28390BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28390BC\"></sup> by human standards; not many were influential; not many were of noble birth.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But God chose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28391BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28391BD\"></sup> the foolish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28391BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28391BE\"></sup> things of the world to shame the wise; God chose the weak things of the world to shame the strong.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>God chose the lowly things of this world and the despised things—and the things that are not<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28392BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28392BF\"></sup>—to nullify the things that are,",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>so that no one may boast before him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28393BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28393BG\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>It is because of him that you are in Christ Jesus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28394BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28394BH\"></sup> who has become for us wisdom from God—that is, our righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28394BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28394BI\"></sup> holiness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28394BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28394BJ\"></sup> and redemption.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28394BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28394BK\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Therefore, as it is written: “Let the one who boasts boast in the Lord.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28395BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28395BL\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>And so it was with me, brothers and sisters. When I came to you, I did not come with eloquence or human wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28396A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28396A\"></sup> as I proclaimed to you the testimony about God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For I resolved to know nothing while I was with you except Jesus Christ and him crucified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28397B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28397B\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I came to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28398C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28398C\"></sup> in weakness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28398D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28398D\"></sup> with great fear and trembling.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28398E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28398E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My message and my preaching were not with wise and persuasive words,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28399F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28399F\"></sup> but with a demonstration of the Spirit’s power,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28399G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28399G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>so that your faith might not rest on human wisdom, but on God’s power.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28400H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28400H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>We do, however, speak a message of wisdom among the mature,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28401I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28401I\"></sup> but not the wisdom of this age<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28401J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28401J\"></sup> or of the rulers of this age, who are coming to nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28401K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28401K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>No, we declare God’s wisdom, a mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28402L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28402L\"></sup> that has been hidden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28402M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28402M\"></sup> and that God destined for our glory before time began.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>None of the rulers of this age<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28403N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28403N\"></sup> understood it, for if they had, they would not have crucified the Lord of glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28403O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28403O\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>However, as it is written:“What no eye has seen,what no ear has heard,and what no human mind has conceived”—the things God has prepared for those who love him—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28404P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28404P\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>these are the things God has revealed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28405Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28405Q\"></sup> to us by his Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28405R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28405R\"></sup>The Spirit searches all things, even the deep things of God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For who knows a person’s thoughts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28406S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28406S\"></sup> except their own spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28406T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28406T\"></sup> within them? In the same way no one knows the thoughts of God except the Spirit of God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>What we have received is not the spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28407U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28407U\"></sup> of the world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28407V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28407V\"></sup> but the Spirit who is from God, so that we may understand what God has freely given us.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is what we speak, not in words taught us by human wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28408W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28408W\"></sup> but in words taught by the Spirit, explaining spiritual realities with Spirit-taught words.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The person without the Spirit does not accept the things that come from the Spirit of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28409X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28409X\"></sup> but considers them foolishness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28409Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28409Y\"></sup> and cannot understand them because they are discerned only through the Spirit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The person with the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28410Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28410Z\"></sup> makes judgments about all things, but such a person is not subject to merely human judgments,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>for,“Who has known the mind of the Lordso as to instruct him?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28411AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28411AA\"></sup>But we have the mind of Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28411AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28411AB\"></sup>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Brothers and sisters, I could not address you as people who live by the Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28412A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28412A\"></sup> but as people who are still worldly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28412B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28412B\"></sup>—mere infants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28412C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28412C\"></sup> in Christ.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I gave you milk, not solid food,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28413D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28413D\"></sup> for you were not yet ready for it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28413E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28413E\"></sup> Indeed, you are still not ready.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You are still worldly. For since there is jealousy and quarreling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28414F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28414F\"></sup> among you, are you not worldly? Are you not acting like mere humans?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For when one says, “I follow Paul,” and another, “I follow Apollos,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28415G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28415G\"></sup> are you not mere human beings?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>What, after all, is Apollos?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28416H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28416H\"></sup> And what is Paul? Only servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28416I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28416I\"></sup> through whom you came to believe—as the Lord has assigned to each his task.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I planted the seed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28417J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28417J\"></sup> Apollos watered it, but God has been making it grow.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So neither the one who plants nor the one who waters is anything, but only God, who makes things grow.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The one who plants and the one who waters have one purpose, and they will each be rewarded according to their own labor.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28419K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28419K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For we are co-workers in God’s service;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28420L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28420L\"></sup> you are God’s field,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28420M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28420M\"></sup> God’s building.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28420N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28420N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>By the grace God has given me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28421O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28421O\"></sup> I laid a foundation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28421P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28421P\"></sup> as a wise builder, and someone else is building on it. But each one should build with care.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For no one can lay any foundation other than the one already laid, which is Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28422Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28422Q\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If anyone builds on this foundation using gold, silver, costly stones, wood, hay or straw,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>their work will be shown for what it is,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28424R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28424R\"></sup> because the Day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28424S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28424S\"></sup> will bring it to light. It will be revealed with fire, and the fire will test the quality of each person’s work.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28424T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28424T\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>If what has been built survives, the builder will receive a reward.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28425U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28425U\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>If it is burned up, the builder will suffer loss but yet will be saved—even though only as one escaping through the flames.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28426V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28426V\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Don’t you know that you yourselves are God’s temple<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28427W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28427W\"></sup> and that God’s Spirit dwells in your midst?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28427X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28427X\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If anyone destroys God’s temple, God will destroy that person; for God’s temple is sacred, and you together are that temple.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Do not deceive yourselves. If any of you think you are wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28429Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28429Y\"></sup> by the standards of this age,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28429Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28429Z\"></sup> you should become “fools” so that you may become wise.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For the wisdom of this world is foolishness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28430AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28430AA\"></sup> in God’s sight. As it is written: “He catches the wise in their craftiness”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28430AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28430AB\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and again, “The Lord knows that the thoughts of the wise are futile.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28431AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28431AC\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So then, no more boasting about human leaders!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28432AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28432AD\"></sup> All things are yours,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28432AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28432AE\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>whether Paul or Apollos<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28433AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28433AF\"></sup> or Cephas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28433AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28433AG\"></sup> or the world or life or death or the present or the future<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28433AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28433AH\"></sup>—all are yours,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and you are of Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28434AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28434AI\"></sup> and Christ is of God."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>This, then, is how you ought to regard us: as servants<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28435A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28435A\"></sup> of Christ and as those entrusted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28435B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28435B\"></sup> with the mysteries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28435C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28435C\"></sup> God has revealed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now it is required that those who have been given a trust must prove faithful.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I care very little if I am judged by you or by any human court; indeed, I do not even judge myself.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My conscience<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28438D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28438D\"></sup> is clear, but that does not make me innocent.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28438E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28438E\"></sup> It is the Lord who judges me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28438F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28438F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore judge nothing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28439G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28439G\"></sup> before the appointed time; wait until the Lord comes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28439H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28439H\"></sup> He will bring to light<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28439I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28439I\"></sup> what is hidden in darkness and will expose the motives of the heart. At that time each will receive their praise from God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28439J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28439J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now, brothers and sisters, I have applied these things to myself and Apollos for your benefit, so that you may learn from us the meaning of the saying, “Do not go beyond what is written.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28440K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28440K\"></sup> Then you will not be puffed up in being a follower of one of us over against the other.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28440L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28440L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For who makes you different from anyone else? What do you have that you did not receive?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28441M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28441M\"></sup> And if you did receive it, why do you boast as though you did not?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Already you have all you want! Already you have become rich!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28442N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28442N\"></sup> You have begun to reign—and that without us! How I wish that you really had begun to reign so that we also might reign with you!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For it seems to me that God has put us apostles on display at the end of the procession, like those condemned to die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28443O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28443O\"></sup> in the arena. We have been made a spectacle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28443P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28443P\"></sup> to the whole universe, to angels as well as to human beings.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We are fools for Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28444Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28444Q\"></sup> but you are so wise in Christ!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28444R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28444R\"></sup> We are weak, but you are strong!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28444S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28444S\"></sup> You are honored, we are dishonored!",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>To this very hour we go hungry and thirsty, we are in rags, we are brutally treated, we are homeless.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28445T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28445T\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>We work hard with our own hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28446U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28446U\"></sup> When we are cursed, we bless;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28446V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28446V\"></sup> when we are persecuted,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28446W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28446W\"></sup> we endure it;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>when we are slandered, we answer kindly. We have become the scum of the earth, the garbage<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28447X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28447X\"></sup> of the world—right up to this moment.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I am writing this not to shame you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28448Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28448Y\"></sup> but to warn you as my dear children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28448Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28448Z\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Even if you had ten thousand guardians in Christ, you do not have many fathers, for in Christ Jesus I became your father<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28449AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28449AA\"></sup> through the gospel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28449AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28449AB\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore I urge you to imitate me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28450AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28450AC\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For this reason I have sent to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28451AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28451AD\"></sup> Timothy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28451AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28451AE\"></sup> my son<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28451AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28451AF\"></sup> whom I love, who is faithful in the Lord. He will remind you of my way of life in Christ Jesus, which agrees with what I teach everywhere in every church.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28451AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28451AG\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Some of you have become arrogant,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28452AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28452AH\"></sup> as if I were not coming to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28452AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28452AI\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But I will come to you very soon,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28453AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28453AJ\"></sup> if the Lord is willing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28453AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28453AK\"></sup> and then I will find out not only how these arrogant people are talking, but what power they have.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For the kingdom of God is not a matter of<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28454AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28454AL\"></sup> talk but of power.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28454AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28454AM\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>What do you prefer? Shall I come to you with a rod of discipline,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28455AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28455AN\"></sup> or shall I come in love and with a gentle spirit?"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>It is actually reported that there is sexual immorality among you, and of a kind that even pagans do not tolerate: A man is sleeping with his father’s wife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28456A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28456A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And you are proud! Shouldn’t you rather have gone into mourning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28457B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28457B\"></sup> and have put out of your fellowship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28457C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28457C\"></sup> the man who has been doing this?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For my part, even though I am not physically present, I am with you in spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28458D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28458D\"></sup> As one who is present with you in this way, I have already passed judgment in the name of our Lord Jesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28458E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28458E\"></sup> on the one who has been doing this.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So when you are assembled and I am with you in spirit, and the power of our Lord Jesus is present,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>hand this man over<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28460F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28460F\"></sup> to Satan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28460G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28460G\"></sup> for the destruction of the flesh, so that his spirit may be saved on the day of the Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28460H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28460H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Your boasting is not good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28461I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28461I\"></sup> Don’t you know that a little yeast<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28461J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28461J\"></sup> leavens the whole batch of dough?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28461K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28461K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Get rid of the old yeast, so that you may be a new unleavened batch—as you really are. For Christ, our Passover lamb, has been sacrificed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28462L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28462L\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore let us keep the Festival, not with the old bread leavened with malice and wickedness, but with the unleavened bread<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28463M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28463M\"></sup> of sincerity and truth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I wrote to you in my letter not to associate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28464N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28464N\"></sup> with sexually immoral people—",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>not at all meaning the people of this world<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28465O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28465O\"></sup> who are immoral, or the greedy and swindlers, or idolaters. In that case you would have to leave this world.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But now I am writing to you that you must not associate with anyone who claims to be a brother or sister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28466P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28466P\"></sup> but is sexually immoral or greedy, an idolater<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28466Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28466Q\"></sup> or slanderer, a drunkard or swindler. Do not even eat with such people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28466R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28466R\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>What business is it of mine to judge those outside<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28467S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28467S\"></sup> the church? Are you not to judge those inside?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28467T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28467T\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>God will judge those outside. “Expel the wicked person from among you.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28468U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28468U\"></sup>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>If any of you has a dispute with another, do you dare to take it before the ungodly for judgment instead of before the Lord’s people?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28469A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28469A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Or do you not know that the Lord’s people will judge the world?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28470B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28470B\"></sup> And if you are to judge the world, are you not competent to judge trivial cases?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Do you not know that we will judge angels? How much more the things of this life!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore, if you have disputes about such matters, do you ask for a ruling from those whose way of life is scorned in the church?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I say this to shame you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28473C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28473C\"></sup> Is it possible that there is nobody among you wise enough to judge a dispute between believers?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28473D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28473D\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But instead, one brother<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28474E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28474E\"></sup> takes another to court—and this in front of unbelievers!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28474F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28474F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The very fact that you have lawsuits among you means you have been completely defeated already. Why not rather be wronged? Why not rather be cheated?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28475G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28475G\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Instead, you yourselves cheat and do wrong, and you do this to your brothers and sisters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28476H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28476H\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Or do you not know that wrongdoers will not inherit the kingdom of God?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28477I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28477I\"></sup> Do not be deceived:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28477J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28477J\"></sup> Neither the sexually immoral nor idolaters nor adulterers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28477K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28477K\"></sup> nor men who have sex with men<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28477L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28477L\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>nor thieves nor the greedy nor drunkards nor slanderers nor swindlers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28478M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28478M\"></sup> will inherit the kingdom of God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And that is what some of you were.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28479N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28479N\"></sup> But you were washed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28479O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28479O\"></sup> you were sanctified,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28479P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28479P\"></sup> you were justified<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28479Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28479Q\"></sup> in the name of the Lord Jesus Christ and by the Spirit of our God.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I have the right to do anything,” you say—but not everything is beneficial.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28480R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28480R\"></sup> “I have the right to do anything”—but I will not be mastered by anything.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>You say, “Food for the stomach and the stomach for food, and God will destroy them both.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28481S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28481S\"></sup> The body, however, is not meant for sexual immorality but for the Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28481T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28481T\"></sup> and the Lord for the body.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>By his power God raised the Lord from the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28482U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28482U\"></sup> and he will raise us also.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28482V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28482V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Do you not know that your bodies are members of Christ himself?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28483W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28483W\"></sup> Shall I then take the members of Christ and unite them with a prostitute? Never!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Do you not know that he who unites himself with a prostitute is one with her in body? For it is said, “The two will become one flesh.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28484X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28484X\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But whoever is united with the Lord is one with him in spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28485Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28485Y\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Flee from sexual immorality.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28486Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28486Z\"></sup> All other sins a person commits are outside the body, but whoever sins sexually, sins against their own body.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28486AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28486AA\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do you not know that your bodies are temples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28487AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28487AB\"></sup> of the Holy Spirit, who is in you, whom you have received from God? You are not your own;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28487AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28487AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>you were bought at a price.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28488AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28488AD\"></sup> Therefore honor God with your bodies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28488AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28488AE\"></sup>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Now for the matters you wrote about: “It is good for a man not to have sexual relations with a woman.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28489A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28489A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But since sexual immorality is occurring, each man should have sexual relations with his own wife, and each woman with her own husband.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The husband should fulfill his marital duty to his wife,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28491B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28491B\"></sup> and likewise the wife to her husband.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The wife does not have authority over her own body but yields it to her husband. In the same way, the husband does not have authority over his own body but yields it to his wife.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Do not deprive each other except perhaps by mutual consent and for a time,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28493C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28493C\"></sup> so that you may devote yourselves to prayer. Then come together again so that Satan<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28493D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28493D\"></sup> will not tempt you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28493E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28493E\"></sup> because of your lack of self-control.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I say this as a concession, not as a command.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28494F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28494F\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I wish that all of you were as I am.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28495G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28495G\"></sup> But each of you has your own gift from God; one has this gift, another has that.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28495H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28495H\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now to the unmarried and the widows I say: It is good for them to stay unmarried, as I do.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28496I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28496I\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But if they cannot control themselves, they should marry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28497J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28497J\"></sup> for it is better to marry than to burn with passion.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>To the married I give this command (not I, but the Lord): A wife must not separate from her husband.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28498K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28498K\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But if she does, she must remain unmarried or else be reconciled to her husband.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28499L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28499L\"></sup> And a husband must not divorce his wife.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>To the rest I say this (I, not the Lord):<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28500M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28500M\"></sup> If any brother has a wife who is not a believer and she is willing to live with him, he must not divorce her.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And if a woman has a husband who is not a believer and he is willing to live with her, she must not divorce him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the unbelieving husband has been sanctified through his wife, and the unbelieving wife has been sanctified through her believing husband. Otherwise your children would be unclean, but as it is, they are holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28502N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28502N\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But if the unbeliever leaves, let it be so. The brother or the sister is not bound in such circumstances; God has called us to live in peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28503O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28503O\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>How do you know, wife, whether you will save<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28504P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28504P\"></sup> your husband?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28504Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28504Q\"></sup> Or, how do you know, husband, whether you will save your wife?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Nevertheless, each person should live as a believer in whatever situation the Lord has assigned to them, just as God has called them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28505R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28505R\"></sup> This is the rule I lay down in all the churches.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28505S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28505S\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Was a man already circumcised when he was called? He should not become uncircumcised. Was a man uncircumcised when he was called? He should not be circumcised.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28506T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28506T\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Circumcision is nothing and uncircumcision is nothing.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28507U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28507U\"></sup> Keeping God’s commands is what counts.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Each person should remain in the situation they were in when God called them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28508V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28508V\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Were you a slave when you were called? Don’t let it trouble you—although if you can gain your freedom, do so.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For the one who was a slave when called to faith in the Lord is the Lord’s freed person;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28510W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28510W\"></sup> similarly, the one who was free when called is Christ’s slave.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28510X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28510X\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>You were bought at a price;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28511Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28511Y\"></sup> do not become slaves of human beings.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Brothers and sisters, each person, as responsible to God, should remain in the situation they were in when God called them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28512Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28512Z\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now about virgins: I have no command from the Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28513AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28513AA\"></sup> but I give a judgment as one who by the Lord’s mercy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28513AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28513AB\"></sup> is trustworthy.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Because of the present crisis, I think that it is good for a man to remain as he is.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28514AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28514AC\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Are you pledged to a woman? Do not seek to be released. Are you free from such a commitment? Do not look for a wife.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28515AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28515AD\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if you do marry, you have not sinned;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28516AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28516AE\"></sup> and if a virgin marries, she has not sinned. But those who marry will face many troubles in this life, and I want to spare you this.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>What I mean, brothers and sisters, is that the time is short.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28517AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28517AF\"></sup> From now on those who have wives should live as if they do not;",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>those who mourn, as if they did not; those who are happy, as if they were not; those who buy something, as if it were not theirs to keep;",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>those who use the things of the world, as if not engrossed in them. For this world in its present form is passing away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28519AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28519AG\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>I would like you to be free from concern. An unmarried man is concerned about the Lord’s affairs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28520AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28520AH\"></sup>—how he can please the Lord.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But a married man is concerned about the affairs of this world—how he can please his wife—",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>and his interests are divided. An unmarried woman or virgin is concerned about the Lord’s affairs: Her aim is to be devoted to the Lord in both body and spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28522AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28522AI\"></sup> But a married woman is concerned about the affairs of this world—how she can please her husband.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>I am saying this for your own good, not to restrict you, but that you may live in a right way in undivided<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28523AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28523AJ\"></sup> devotion to the Lord.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>If anyone is worried that he might not be acting honorably toward the virgin he is engaged to, and if his passions are too strong and he feels he ought to marry, he should do as he wants. He is not sinning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28524AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28524AK\"></sup> They should get married.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But the man who has settled the matter in his own mind, who is under no compulsion but has control over his own will, and who has made up his mind not to marry the virgin—this man also does the right thing.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>So then, he who marries the virgin does right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28526AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28526AL\"></sup> but he who does not marry her does better.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>A woman is bound to her husband as long as he lives.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28527AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28527AM\"></sup> But if her husband dies, she is free to marry anyone she wishes, but he must belong to the Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28527AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28527AN\"></sup>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>In my judgment,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28528AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28528AO\"></sup> she is happier if she stays as she is—and I think that I too have the Spirit of God."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Now about food sacrificed to idols:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28529A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28529A\"></sup> We know that “We all possess knowledge.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28529B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28529B\"></sup> But knowledge puffs up while love builds up.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Those who think they know something<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28530C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28530C\"></sup> do not yet know as they ought to know.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28530D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28530D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But whoever loves God is known by God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28531E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28531E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So then, about eating food sacrificed to idols:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28532F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28532F\"></sup> We know that “An idol is nothing at all in the world”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28532G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28532G\"></sup> and that “There is no God but one.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28532H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28532H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For even if there are so-called gods,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28533I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28533I\"></sup> whether in heaven or on earth (as indeed there are many “gods” and many “lords”),",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>yet for us there is but one God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28534J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28534J\"></sup> the Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28534K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28534K\"></sup> from whom all things came<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28534L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28534L\"></sup> and for whom we live; and there is but one Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28534M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28534M\"></sup> Jesus Christ, through whom all things came<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28534N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28534N\"></sup> and through whom we live.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But not everyone possesses this knowledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28535O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28535O\"></sup> Some people are still so accustomed to idols that when they eat sacrificial food they think of it as having been sacrificed to a god, and since their conscience is weak,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28535P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28535P\"></sup> it is defiled.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But food does not bring us near to God;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28536Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28536Q\"></sup> we are no worse if we do not eat, and no better if we do.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Be careful, however, that the exercise of your rights does not become a stumbling block<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28537R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28537R\"></sup> to the weak.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28537S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28537S\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For if someone with a weak conscience sees you, with all your knowledge, eating in an idol’s temple, won’t that person be emboldened to eat what is sacrificed to idols?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28538T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28538T\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So this weak brother or sister, for whom Christ died, is destroyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28539U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28539U\"></sup> by your knowledge.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When you sin against them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28540V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28540V\"></sup> in this way and wound their weak conscience, you sin against Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28540W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28540W\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, if what I eat causes my brother or sister to fall into sin, I will never eat meat again, so that I will not cause them to fall.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28541X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28541X\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Am I not free?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28542A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28542A\"></sup> Am I not an apostle?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28542B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28542B\"></sup> Have I not seen Jesus our Lord?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28542C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28542C\"></sup> Are you not the result of my work in the Lord?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28542D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28542D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Even though I may not be an apostle to others, surely I am to you! For you are the seal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28543E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28543E\"></sup> of my apostleship in the Lord.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>This is my defense to those who sit in judgment on me.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Don’t we have the right to food and drink?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28545F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28545F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Don’t we have the right to take a believing wife<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28546G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28546G\"></sup> along with us, as do the other apostles and the Lord’s brothers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28546H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28546H\"></sup> and Cephas?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28546I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28546I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Or is it only I and Barnabas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28547J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28547J\"></sup> who lack the right to not work for a living?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Who serves as a soldier<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28548K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28548K\"></sup> at his own expense? Who plants a vineyard<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28548L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28548L\"></sup> and does not eat its grapes? Who tends a flock and does not drink the milk?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Do I say this merely on human authority? Doesn’t the Law say the same thing?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For it is written in the Law of Moses: “Do not muzzle an ox while it is treading out the grain.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28550M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28550M\"></sup> Is it about oxen that God is concerned?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28550N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28550N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Surely he says this for us, doesn’t he? Yes, this was written for us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28551O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28551O\"></sup> because whoever plows and threshes should be able to do so in the hope of sharing in the harvest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28551P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28551P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If we have sown spiritual seed among you, is it too much if we reap a material harvest from you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28552Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28552Q\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>If others have this right of support from you, shouldn’t we have it all the more?But we did not use this right.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28553R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28553R\"></sup> On the contrary, we put up with anything rather than hinder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28553S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28553S\"></sup> the gospel of Christ.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Don’t you know that those who serve in the temple get their food from the temple, and that those who serve at the altar share in what is offered on the altar?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28554T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28554T\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>In the same way, the Lord has commanded that those who preach the gospel should receive their living from the gospel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28555U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28555U\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But I have not used any of these rights.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28556V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28556V\"></sup> And I am not writing this in the hope that you will do such things for me, for I would rather die than allow anyone to deprive me of this boast.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28556W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28556W\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For when I preach the gospel, I cannot boast, since I am compelled to preach.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28557X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28557X\"></sup> Woe to me if I do not preach the gospel!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If I preach voluntarily, I have a reward;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28558Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28558Y\"></sup> if not voluntarily, I am simply discharging the trust committed to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28558Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28558Z\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>What then is my reward? Just this: that in preaching the gospel I may offer it free of charge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28559AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28559AA\"></sup> and so not make full use of my rights<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28559AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28559AB\"></sup> as a preacher of the gospel.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Though I am free<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28560AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28560AC\"></sup> and belong to no one, I have made myself a slave to everyone,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28560AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28560AD\"></sup> to win as many as possible.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28560AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28560AE\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>To the Jews I became like a Jew, to win the Jews.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28561AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28561AF\"></sup> To those under the law I became like one under the law (though I myself am not under the law),<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28561AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28561AG\"></sup> so as to win those under the law.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>To those not having the law I became like one not having the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28562AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28562AH\"></sup> (though I am not free from God’s law but am under Christ’s law),<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28562AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28562AI\"></sup> so as to win those not having the law.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>To the weak I became weak, to win the weak.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28563AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28563AJ\"></sup> I have become all things to all people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28563AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28563AK\"></sup> so that by all possible means I might save some.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28563AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28563AL\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I do all this for the sake of the gospel, that I may share in its blessings.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Do you not know that in a race all the runners run, but only one gets the prize?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28565AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28565AM\"></sup> Run<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28565AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28565AN\"></sup> in such a way as to get the prize.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Everyone who competes in the games goes into strict training. They do it to get a crown<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28566AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28566AO\"></sup> that will not last, but we do it to get a crown that will last forever.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28566AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28566AP\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Therefore I do not run like someone running aimlessly;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28567AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28567AQ\"></sup> I do not fight like a boxer beating the air.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28567AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28567AR\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>No, I strike a blow to my body<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28568AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28568AS\"></sup> and make it my slave so that after I have preached to others, I myself will not be disqualified for the prize.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28568AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28568AT\"></sup>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>For I do not want you to be ignorant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28569A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28569A\"></sup> of the fact, brothers and sisters, that our ancestors were all under the cloud<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28569B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28569B\"></sup> and that they all passed through the sea.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28569C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28569C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They were all baptized into<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28570D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28570D\"></sup> Moses in the cloud and in the sea.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They all ate the same spiritual food<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28571E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28571E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and drank the same spiritual drink; for they drank from the spiritual rock<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28572F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28572F\"></sup> that accompanied them, and that rock was Christ.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Nevertheless, God was not pleased with most of them; their bodies were scattered in the wilderness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28573G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28573G\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now these things occurred as examples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28574H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28574H\"></sup> to keep us from setting our hearts on evil things as they did.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Do not be idolaters,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28575I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28575I\"></sup> as some of them were; as it is written: “The people sat down to eat and drink and got up to indulge in revelry.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28575J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28575J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>We should not commit sexual immorality, as some of them did—and in one day twenty-three thousand of them died.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28576K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28576K\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>We should not test Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28577L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28577L\"></sup> as some of them did—and were killed by snakes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28577M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28577M\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And do not grumble, as some of them did<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28578N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28578N\"></sup>—and were killed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28578O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28578O\"></sup> by the destroying angel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28578P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28578P\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>These things happened to them as examples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28579Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28579Q\"></sup> and were written down as warnings for us,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28579R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28579R\"></sup> on whom the culmination of the ages has come.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28579S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28579S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So, if you think you are standing firm,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28580T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28580T\"></sup> be careful that you don’t fall!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>No temptation has overtaken you except what is common to mankind. And God is faithful;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28581U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28581U\"></sup> he will not let you be tempted beyond what you can bear.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28581V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28581V\"></sup> But when you are tempted, he will also provide a way out so that you can endure it.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, my dear friends,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28582W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28582W\"></sup> flee from idolatry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28582X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28582X\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I speak to sensible people; judge for yourselves what I say.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Is not the cup of thanksgiving for which we give thanks a participation in the blood of Christ? And is not the bread that we break<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28584Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28584Y\"></sup> a participation in the body of Christ?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28584Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28584Z\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Because there is one loaf, we, who are many, are one body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28585AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28585AA\"></sup> for we all share the one loaf.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Consider the people of Israel: Do not those who eat the sacrifices<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28586AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28586AB\"></sup> participate in the altar?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Do I mean then that food sacrificed to an idol is anything, or that an idol is anything?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28587AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28587AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>No, but the sacrifices of pagans are offered to demons,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28588AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28588AD\"></sup> not to God, and I do not want you to be participants with demons.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>You cannot drink the cup of the Lord and the cup of demons too; you cannot have a part in both the Lord’s table and the table of demons.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28589AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28589AE\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Are we trying to arouse the Lord’s jealousy?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28590AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28590AF\"></sup> Are we stronger than he?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28590AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28590AG\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“I have the right to do anything,” you say—but not everything is beneficial.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28591AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28591AH\"></sup> “I have the right to do anything”—but not everything is constructive.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>No one should seek their own good, but the good of others.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28592AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28592AI\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Eat anything sold in the meat market without raising questions of conscience,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28593AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28593AJ\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>for, “The earth is the Lord’s, and everything in it.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28594AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28594AK\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If an unbeliever invites you to a meal and you want to go, eat whatever is put before you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28595AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28595AL\"></sup> without raising questions of conscience.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But if someone says to you, “This has been offered in sacrifice,” then do not eat it, both for the sake of the one who told you and for the sake of conscience.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28596AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28596AM\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>I am referring to the other person’s conscience, not yours. For why is my freedom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28597AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28597AN\"></sup> being judged by another’s conscience?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>If I take part in the meal with thankfulness, why am I denounced because of something I thank God for?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28598AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28598AO\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So whether you eat or drink or whatever you do, do it all for the glory of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28599AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28599AP\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Do not cause anyone to stumble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28600AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28600AQ\"></sup> whether Jews, Greeks or the church of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28600AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28600AR\"></sup>—",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>even as I try to please everyone in every way.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28601AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28601AS\"></sup> For I am not seeking my own good but the good of many,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28601AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28601AT\"></sup> so that they may be saved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28601AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28601AU\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum mid-paragraph\">11 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-paragraph\">1 </sup>Follow my example,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28602A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28602A\"></sup> as I follow the example of Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28602B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28602B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I praise you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28603C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28603C\"></sup> for remembering me in everything<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28603D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28603D\"></sup> and for holding to the traditions just as I passed them on to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28603E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28603E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But I want you to realize that the head of every man is Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28604F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28604F\"></sup> and the head of the woman is man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28604G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28604G\"></sup> and the head of Christ is God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28604H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28604H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Every man who prays or prophesies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28605I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28605I\"></sup> with his head covered dishonors his head.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But every woman who prays or prophesies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28606J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28606J\"></sup> with her head uncovered dishonors her head—it is the same as having her head shaved.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28606K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28606K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For if a woman does not cover her head, she might as well have her hair cut off; but if it is a disgrace for a woman to have her hair cut off or her head shaved, then she should cover her head.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>A man ought not to cover his head, since he is the image<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28608L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28608L\"></sup> and glory of God; but woman is the glory of man.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For man did not come from woman, but woman from man;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28609M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28609M\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>neither was man created for woman, but woman for man.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28610N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28610N\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>It is for this reason that a woman ought to have authority over her own head, because of the angels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Nevertheless, in the Lord woman is not independent of man, nor is man independent of woman.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For as woman came from man, so also man is born of woman. But everything comes from God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28613O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28613O\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Judge for yourselves: Is it proper for a woman to pray to God with her head uncovered?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Does not the very nature of things teach you that if a man has long hair, it is a disgrace to him,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but that if a woman has long hair, it is her glory? For long hair is given to her as a covering.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>If anyone wants to be contentious about this, we have no other practice—nor do the churches of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28617P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28617P\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the following directives I have no praise for you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28618R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28618R\"></sup> for your meetings do more harm than good.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In the first place, I hear that when you come together as a church, there are divisions<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28619S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28619S\"></sup> among you, and to some extent I believe it.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>No doubt there have to be differences among you to show which of you have God’s approval.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28620T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28620T\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So then, when you come together, it is not the Lord’s Supper you eat,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for when you are eating, some of you go ahead with your own private suppers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28622U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28622U\"></sup> As a result, one person remains hungry and another gets drunk.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Don’t you have homes to eat and drink in? Or do you despise the church of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28623V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28623V\"></sup> by humiliating those who have nothing?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28623W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28623W\"></sup> What shall I say to you? Shall I praise you?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28623X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28623X\"></sup> Certainly not in this matter!",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For I received from the Lord<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28624Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28624Y\"></sup> what I also passed on to you:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28624Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28624Z\"></sup> The Lord Jesus, on the night he was betrayed, took bread,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and when he had given thanks, he broke it and said, <span class=\"woj\">“This is my body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28625AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28625AA\"></sup> which is for you; do this in remembrance of me.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In the same way, after supper he took the cup, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“This cup is the new covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28626AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28626AB\"></sup> in my blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28626AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28626AC\"></sup> do this, whenever you drink it, in remembrance of me.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For whenever you eat this bread and drink this cup, you proclaim the Lord’s death until he comes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28627AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28627AD\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So then, whoever eats the bread or drinks the cup of the Lord in an unworthy manner will be guilty of sinning against the body and blood of the Lord.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28628AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28628AE\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Everyone ought to examine themselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28629AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28629AF\"></sup> before they eat of the bread and drink from the cup.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>For those who eat and drink without discerning the body of Christ eat and drink judgment on themselves.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>That is why many among you are weak and sick, and a number of you have fallen asleep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28631AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28631AG\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But if we were more discerning with regard to ourselves, we would not come under such judgment.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28632AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28632AH\"></sup>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Nevertheless, when we are judged in this way by the Lord, we are being disciplined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28633AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28633AI\"></sup> so that we will not be finally condemned with the world.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28633AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28633AJ\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>So then, my brothers and sisters, when you gather to eat, you should all eat together.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Anyone who is hungry<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28635AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28635AK\"></sup> should eat something at home,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28635AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28635AL\"></sup> so that when you meet together it may not result in judgment.And when I come<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28635AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28635AM\"></sup> I will give further directions."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Now about the gifts of the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28636A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28636A\"></sup> brothers and sisters, I do not want you to be uninformed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28636B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28636B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>You know that when you were pagans,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28637C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28637C\"></sup> somehow or other you were influenced and led astray to mute idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28637D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28637D\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore I want you to know that no one who is speaking by the Spirit of God says, “Jesus be cursed,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28638E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28638E\"></sup> and no one can say, “Jesus is Lord,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28638F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28638F\"></sup> except by the Holy Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28638G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28638G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>There are different kinds of gifts, but the same Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28639H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28639H\"></sup> distributes them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>There are different kinds of service, but the same Lord.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There are different kinds of working, but in all of them and in everyone<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28641I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28641I\"></sup> it is the same God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28641J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28641J\"></sup> at work.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now to each one the manifestation of the Spirit is given for the common good.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28642K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28642K\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>To one there is given through the Spirit a message of wisdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28643L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28643L\"></sup> to another a message of knowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28643M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28643M\"></sup> by means of the same Spirit,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>to another faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28644N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28644N\"></sup> by the same Spirit, to another gifts of healing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28644O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28644O\"></sup> by that one Spirit,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>to another miraculous powers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28645P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28645P\"></sup> to another prophecy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28645Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28645Q\"></sup> to another distinguishing between spirits,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28645R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28645R\"></sup> to another speaking in different kinds of tongues,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28645S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28645S\"></sup> and to still another the interpretation of tongues.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All these are the work of one and the same Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28646T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28646T\"></sup> and he distributes them to each one, just as he determines.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Just as a body, though one, has many parts, but all its many parts form one body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28647U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28647U\"></sup> so it is with Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28647V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28647V\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For we were all baptized<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28648W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28648W\"></sup> by one Spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28648X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28648X\"></sup> so as to form one body—whether Jews or Gentiles, slave or free<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28648Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28648Y\"></sup>—and we were all given the one Spirit to drink.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28648Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28648Z\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Even so the body is not made up of one part but of many.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28649AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28649AA\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now if the foot should say, “Because I am not a hand, I do not belong to the body,” it would not for that reason stop being part of the body.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And if the ear should say, “Because I am not an eye, I do not belong to the body,” it would not for that reason stop being part of the body.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If the whole body were an eye, where would the sense of hearing be? If the whole body were an ear, where would the sense of smell be?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But in fact God has placed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28653AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28653AB\"></sup> the parts in the body, every one of them, just as he wanted them to be.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28653AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28653AC\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If they were all one part, where would the body be?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As it is, there are many parts, but one body.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28655AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28655AD\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The eye cannot say to the hand, “I don’t need you!” And the head cannot say to the feet, “I don’t need you!”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>On the contrary, those parts of the body that seem to be weaker are indispensable,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and the parts that we think are less honorable we treat with special honor. And the parts that are unpresentable are treated with special modesty,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>while our presentable parts need no special treatment. But God has put the body together, giving greater honor to the parts that lacked it,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>so that there should be no division in the body, but that its parts should have equal concern for each other.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If one part suffers, every part suffers with it; if one part is honored, every part rejoices with it.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Now you are the body of Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28662AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28662AE\"></sup> and each one of you is a part of it.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28662AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28662AF\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And God has placed in the church<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28663AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28663AG\"></sup> first of all apostles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28663AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28663AH\"></sup> second prophets,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28663AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28663AI\"></sup> third teachers, then miracles, then gifts of healing,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28663AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28663AJ\"></sup> of helping, of guidance,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28663AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28663AK\"></sup> and of different kinds of tongues.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28663AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28663AL\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Are all apostles? Are all prophets? Are all teachers? Do all work miracles?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Do all have gifts of healing? Do all speak in tongues?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28665AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28665AM\"></sup> Do all interpret?",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Now eagerly desire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28666AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28666AN\"></sup> the greater gifts.And yet I will show you the most excellent way."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>If I speak in the tongues<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28667A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28667A\"></sup> of men or of angels, but do not have love, I am only a resounding gong or a clanging cymbal.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>If I have the gift of prophecy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28668B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28668B\"></sup> and can fathom all mysteries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28668C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28668C\"></sup> and all knowledge,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28668D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28668D\"></sup> and if I have a faith<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28668E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28668E\"></sup> that can move mountains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28668F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28668F\"></sup> but do not have love, I am nothing.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If I give all I possess to the poor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28669G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28669G\"></sup> and give over my body to hardship that I may boast,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28669H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28669H\"></sup> but do not have love, I gain nothing.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Love is patient,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28670I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28670I\"></sup> love is kind. It does not envy, it does not boast, it is not proud.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28670J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28670J\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It does not dishonor others, it is not self-seeking,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28671K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28671K\"></sup> it is not easily angered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28671L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28671L\"></sup> it keeps no record of wrongs.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28671M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28671M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Love does not delight in evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28672N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28672N\"></sup> but rejoices with the truth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28672O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28672O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>It always protects, always trusts, always hopes, always perseveres.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28673P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28673P\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Love never fails. But where there are prophecies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28674Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28674Q\"></sup> they will cease; where there are tongues,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28674R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28674R\"></sup> they will be stilled; where there is knowledge, it will pass away.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For we know in part<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28675S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28675S\"></sup> and we prophesy in part,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>but when completeness comes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28676T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28676T\"></sup> what is in part disappears.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When I was a child, I talked like a child, I thought like a child, I reasoned like a child. When I became a man, I put the ways of childhood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28677U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28677U\"></sup> behind me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For now we see only a reflection as in a mirror;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28678V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28678V\"></sup> then we shall see face to face.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28678W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28678W\"></sup> Now I know in part; then I shall know fully, even as I am fully known.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28678X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28678X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And now these three remain: faith, hope and love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28679Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28679Y\"></sup> But the greatest of these is love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28679Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28679Z\"></sup>"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Follow the way of love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28680A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28680A\"></sup> and eagerly desire<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28680B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28680B\"></sup> gifts of the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28680C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28680C\"></sup> especially prophecy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28680D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28680D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For anyone who speaks in a tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28681E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28681E\"></sup> does not speak to people but to God. Indeed, no one understands them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28681F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28681F\"></sup> they utter mysteries<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28681G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28681G\"></sup> by the Spirit.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But the one who prophesies speaks to people for their strengthening,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28682H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28682H\"></sup> encouraging<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28682I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28682I\"></sup> and comfort.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Anyone who speaks in a tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28683J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28683J\"></sup> edifies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28683K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28683K\"></sup> themselves, but the one who prophesies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28683L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28683L\"></sup> edifies the church.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I would like every one of you to speak in tongues, but I would rather have you prophesy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28684M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28684M\"></sup> The one who prophesies is greater than the one who speaks in tongues, unless someone interprets, so that the church may be edified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28684N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28684N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now, brothers and sisters, if I come to you and speak in tongues, what good will I be to you, unless I bring you some revelation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28685O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28685O\"></sup> or knowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28685P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28685P\"></sup> or prophecy or word of instruction?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28685Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28685Q\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Even in the case of lifeless things that make sounds, such as the pipe or harp, how will anyone know what tune is being played unless there is a distinction in the notes?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Again, if the trumpet does not sound a clear call, who will get ready for battle?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28687R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28687R\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So it is with you. Unless you speak intelligible words with your tongue, how will anyone know what you are saying? You will just be speaking into the air.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Undoubtedly there are all sorts of languages in the world, yet none of them is without meaning.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If then I do not grasp the meaning of what someone is saying, I am a foreigner to the speaker, and the speaker is a foreigner to me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28690S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28690S\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So it is with you. Since you are eager for gifts of the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28691T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28691T\"></sup> try to excel in those that build up<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28691U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28691U\"></sup> the church.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For this reason the one who speaks in a tongue should pray that they may interpret what they say.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28692V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28692V\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For if I pray in a tongue, my spirit prays,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28693W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28693W\"></sup> but my mind is unfruitful.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So what shall I do? I will pray with my spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28694X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28694X\"></sup> but I will also pray with my understanding; I will sing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28694Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28694Y\"></sup> with my spirit, but I will also sing with my understanding.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Otherwise when you are praising God in the Spirit, how can someone else, who is now put in the position of an inquirer, say “Amen”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28695Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28695Z\"></sup> to your thanksgiving,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28695AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28695AA\"></sup> since they do not know what you are saying?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You are giving thanks well enough, but no one else is edified.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28696AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28696AB\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I thank God that I speak in tongues more than all of you.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But in the church I would rather speak five intelligible words to instruct others than ten thousand words in a tongue.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28698AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28698AC\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Brothers and sisters, stop thinking like children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28699AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28699AD\"></sup> In regard to evil be infants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28699AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28699AE\"></sup> but in your thinking be adults.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In the Law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28700AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28700AF\"></sup> it is written:“With other tonguesand through the lips of foreignersI will speak to this people,but even then they will not listen to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28700AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28700AG\"></sup>says the Lord.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Tongues, then, are a sign, not for believers but for unbelievers; prophecy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28701AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28701AH\"></sup> however, is not for unbelievers but for believers.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>So if the whole church comes together and everyone speaks in tongues, and inquirers or unbelievers come in, will they not say that you are out of your mind?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28702AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28702AI\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But if an unbeliever or an inquirer comes in while everyone is prophesying, they are convicted of sin and are brought under judgment by all,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>as the secrets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28704AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28704AJ\"></sup> of their hearts are laid bare. So they will fall down and worship God, exclaiming, “God is really among you!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28704AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28704AK\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>What then shall we say, brothers and sisters?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28705AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28705AL\"></sup> When you come together, each of you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28705AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28705AM\"></sup> has a hymn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28705AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28705AN\"></sup> or a word of instruction,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28705AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28705AO\"></sup> a revelation, a tongue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28705AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28705AP\"></sup> or an interpretation.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28705AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28705AQ\"></sup> Everything must be done so that the church may be built up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28705AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28705AR\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If anyone speaks in a tongue, two—or at the most three—should speak, one at a time, and someone must interpret.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>If there is no interpreter, the speaker should keep quiet in the church and speak to himself and to God.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Two or three prophets<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28708AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28708AS\"></sup> should speak, and the others should weigh carefully what is said.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28708AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28708AT\"></sup>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And if a revelation comes to someone who is sitting down, the first speaker should stop.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For you can all prophesy in turn so that everyone may be instructed and encouraged.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>The spirits of prophets are subject to the control of prophets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28711AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28711AU\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For God is not a God of disorder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28712AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28712AV\"></sup> but of peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28712AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28712AW\"></sup>—as in all the congregations<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28712AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28712AX\"></sup> of the Lord’s people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28712AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28712AY\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Women should remain silent in the churches. They are not allowed to speak,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28713AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28713AZ\"></sup> but must be in submission,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28713BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28713BA\"></sup> as the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28713BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28713BB\"></sup> says.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>If they want to inquire about something, they should ask their own husbands at home; for it is disgraceful for a woman to speak in the church.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Or did the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28715BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28715BC\"></sup> originate with you? Or are you the only people it has reached?",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>If anyone thinks they are a prophet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28716BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28716BD\"></sup> or otherwise gifted by the Spirit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28716BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28716BE\"></sup> let them acknowledge that what I am writing to you is the Lord’s command.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28716BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28716BF\"></sup>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But if anyone ignores this, they will themselves be ignored.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Therefore, my brothers and sisters, be eager<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28718BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28718BG\"></sup> to prophesy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28718BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28718BH\"></sup> and do not forbid speaking in tongues.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>But everything should be done in a fitting and orderly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28719BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28719BI\"></sup> way."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Now, brothers and sisters, I want to remind you of the gospel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28720A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28720A\"></sup> I preached to you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28720B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28720B\"></sup> which you received and on which you have taken your stand.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>By this gospel you are saved,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28721C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28721C\"></sup> if you hold firmly<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28721D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28721D\"></sup> to the word I preached to you. Otherwise, you have believed in vain.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For what I received<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28722E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28722E\"></sup> I passed on to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28722F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28722F\"></sup> as of first importance: that Christ died for our sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28722G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28722G\"></sup> according to the Scriptures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28722H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28722H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>that he was buried,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28723I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28723I\"></sup> that he was raised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28723J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28723J\"></sup> on the third day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28723K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28723K\"></sup> according to the Scriptures,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28723L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28723L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and that he appeared to Cephas,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28724M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28724M\"></sup> and then to the Twelve.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28724N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28724N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>After that, he appeared to more than five hundred of the brothers and sisters at the same time, most of whom are still living, though some have fallen asleep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28725O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28725O\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then he appeared to James,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28726P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28726P\"></sup> then to all the apostles,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28726Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28726Q\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and last of all he appeared to me also,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28727R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28727R\"></sup> as to one abnormally born.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For I am the least of the apostles<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28728S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28728S\"></sup> and do not even deserve to be called an apostle, because I persecuted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28728T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28728T\"></sup> the church of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28728U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28728U\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But by the grace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28729V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28729V\"></sup> of God I am what I am, and his grace to me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28729W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28729W\"></sup> was not without effect. No, I worked harder than all of them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28729X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28729X\"></sup>—yet not I, but the grace of God that was with me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28729Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28729Y\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Whether, then, it is I or they,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28730Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28730Z\"></sup> this is what we preach, and this is what you believed.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But if it is preached that Christ has been raised from the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28731AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28731AA\"></sup> how can some of you say that there is no resurrection<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28731AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28731AB\"></sup> of the dead?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28731AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28731AC\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If there is no resurrection of the dead, then not even Christ has been raised.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And if Christ has not been raised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28733AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28733AD\"></sup> our preaching is useless and so is your faith.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>More than that, we are then found to be false witnesses about God, for we have testified about God that he raised Christ from the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28734AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28734AE\"></sup> But he did not raise him if in fact the dead are not raised.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For if the dead are not raised, then Christ has not been raised either.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And if Christ has not been raised, your faith is futile; you are still in your sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28736AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28736AF\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then those also who have fallen asleep<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28737AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28737AG\"></sup> in Christ are lost.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>If only for this life we have hope in Christ, we are of all people most to be pitied.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28738AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28738AH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But Christ has indeed been raised from the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28739AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28739AI\"></sup> the firstfruits<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28739AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28739AJ\"></sup> of those who have fallen asleep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28739AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28739AK\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For since death came through a man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28740AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28740AL\"></sup> the resurrection of the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28740AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28740AM\"></sup> comes also through a man.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For as in Adam all die, so in Christ all will be made alive.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28741AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28741AN\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But each in turn: Christ, the firstfruits;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28742AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28742AO\"></sup> then, when he comes,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28742AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28742AP\"></sup> those who belong to him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28742AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28742AQ\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then the end will come, when he hands over the kingdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28743AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28743AR\"></sup> to God the Father after he has destroyed all dominion, authority and power.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28743AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28743AS\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For he must reign<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28744AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28744AT\"></sup> until he has put all his enemies under his feet.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28744AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28744AU\"></sup>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The last enemy to be destroyed is death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28745AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28745AV\"></sup>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For he “has put everything under his feet.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28746AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28746AW\"></sup> Now when it says that “everything” has been put under him, it is clear that this does not include God himself, who put everything under Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28746AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28746AX\"></sup>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When he has done this, then the Son himself will be made subject to him who put everything under him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28747AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28747AY\"></sup> so that God may be all in all.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28747AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28747AZ\"></sup>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Now if there is no resurrection, what will those do who are baptized for the dead? If the dead are not raised at all, why are people baptized for them?",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And as for us, why do we endanger ourselves every hour?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28749BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28749BA\"></sup>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>I face death every day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28750BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28750BB\"></sup>—yes, just as surely as I boast about you in Christ Jesus our Lord.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>If I fought wild beasts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28751BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28751BC\"></sup> in Ephesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28751BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28751BD\"></sup> with no more than human hopes, what have I gained? If the dead are not raised,“Let us eat and drink,for tomorrow we die.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28751BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28751BE\"></sup>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Do not be misled:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28752BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28752BF\"></sup> “Bad company corrupts good character.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28752BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28752BG\"></sup>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Come back to your senses as you ought, and stop sinning; for there are some who are ignorant of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28753BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28753BH\"></sup>—I say this to your shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28753BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28753BI\"></sup>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>But someone will ask,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28754BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28754BJ\"></sup> “How are the dead raised? With what kind of body will they come?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28754BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28754BK\"></sup>",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>How foolish!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28755BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28755BL\"></sup> What you sow does not come to life unless it dies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28755BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28755BM\"></sup>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>When you sow, you do not plant the body that will be, but just a seed, perhaps of wheat or of something else.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But God gives it a body as he has determined, and to each kind of seed he gives its own body.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28757BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28757BN\"></sup>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>Not all flesh is the same: People have one kind of flesh, animals have another, birds another and fish another.",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>There are also heavenly bodies and there are earthly bodies; but the splendor of the heavenly bodies is one kind, and the splendor of the earthly bodies is another.",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>The sun has one kind of splendor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28760BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28760BO\"></sup> the moon another and the stars another;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28760BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28760BP\"></sup> and star differs from star in splendor.",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>So will it be<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28761BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28761BQ\"></sup> with the resurrection of the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28761BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28761BR\"></sup> The body that is sown is perishable, it is raised imperishable;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28761BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28761BS\"></sup>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>it is sown in dishonor, it is raised in glory;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28762BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28762BT\"></sup> it is sown in weakness, it is raised in power;",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>it is sown a natural body, it is raised a spiritual body.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28763BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28763BU\"></sup>If there is a natural body, there is also a spiritual body.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>So it is written: “The first man Adam became a living being”;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28764BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28764BV\"></sup> the last Adam,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28764BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28764BW\"></sup> a life-giving spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28764BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28764BX\"></sup>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>The spiritual did not come first, but the natural, and after that the spiritual.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28765BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28765BY\"></sup>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>The first man was of the dust of the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28766BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28766BZ\"></sup> the second man is of heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28766CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28766CA\"></sup>",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>As was the earthly man, so are those who are of the earth; and as is the heavenly man, so also are those who are of heaven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28767CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28767CB\"></sup>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And just as we have borne the image of the earthly man,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28768CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28768CC\"></sup> so shall we bear the image of the heavenly man.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28768CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28768CD\"></sup>",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>I declare to you, brothers and sisters, that flesh and blood<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28769CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28769CE\"></sup> cannot inherit the kingdom of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28769CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28769CF\"></sup> nor does the perishable inherit the imperishable.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28769CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28769CG\"></sup>",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>Listen, I tell you a mystery:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28770CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28770CH\"></sup> We will not all sleep,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28770CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28770CI\"></sup> but we will all be changed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28770CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28770CJ\"></sup>—",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>in a flash, in the twinkling of an eye, at the last trumpet. For the trumpet will sound,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28771CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28771CK\"></sup> the dead<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28771CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28771CL\"></sup> will be raised imperishable, and we will be changed.",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>For the perishable<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28772CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28772CM\"></sup> must clothe itself with the imperishable,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28772CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28772CN\"></sup> and the mortal with immortality.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>When the perishable has been clothed with the imperishable, and the mortal with immortality, then the saying that is written will come true: “Death has been swallowed up in victory.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28773CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28773CO\"></sup>",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>“Where, O death, is your victory?Where, O death, is your sting?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28774CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28774CP\"></sup>",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>The sting of death is sin,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28775CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28775CQ\"></sup> and the power of sin is the law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28775CR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CR&quot;&gt;CR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28775CR\"></sup>",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>But thanks be to God!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28776CS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CS&quot;&gt;CS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28776CS\"></sup> He gives us the victory through our Lord Jesus Christ.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28776CT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CT&quot;&gt;CT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28776CT\"></sup>",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>Therefore, my dear brothers and sisters, stand firm. Let nothing move you. Always give yourselves fully to the work of the Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28777CU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CU&quot;&gt;CU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28777CU\"></sup> because you know that your labor in the Lord is not in vain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28777CV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CV&quot;&gt;CV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28777CV\"></sup>"
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Now about the collection<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28778A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28778A\"></sup> for the Lord’s people:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28778B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28778B\"></sup> Do what I told the Galatian<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28778C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28778C\"></sup> churches to do.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>On the first day of every week,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28779D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28779D\"></sup> each one of you should set aside a sum of money in keeping with your income, saving it up, so that when I come no collections will have to be made.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28779E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28779E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then, when I arrive, I will give letters of introduction to the men you approve<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28780F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28780F\"></sup> and send them with your gift to Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>If it seems advisable for me to go also, they will accompany me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>After I go through Macedonia, I will come to you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28782G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28782G\"></sup>—for I will be going through Macedonia.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28782H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28782H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Perhaps I will stay with you for a while, or even spend the winter, so that you can help me on my journey,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28783I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28783I\"></sup> wherever I go.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For I do not want to see you now and make only a passing visit; I hope to spend some time with you, if the Lord permits.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28784J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28784J\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But I will stay on at Ephesus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28785K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28785K\"></sup> until Pentecost,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28785L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28785L\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>because a great door for effective work has opened to me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28786M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28786M\"></sup> and there are many who oppose me.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When Timothy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28787N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28787N\"></sup> comes, see to it that he has nothing to fear while he is with you, for he is carrying on the work of the Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28787O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28787O\"></sup> just as I am.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>No one, then, should treat him with contempt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28788P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28788P\"></sup> Send him on his way<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28788Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28788Q\"></sup> in peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28788R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28788R\"></sup> so that he may return to me. I am expecting him along with the brothers.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now about our brother Apollos:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28789S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28789S\"></sup> I strongly urged him to go to you with the brothers. He was quite unwilling to go now, but he will go when he has the opportunity.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Be on your guard; stand firm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28790T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28790T\"></sup> in the faith; be courageous; be strong.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28790U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28790U\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Do everything in love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28791V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28791V\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>You know that the household of Stephanas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28792W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28792W\"></sup> were the first converts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28792X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28792X\"></sup> in Achaia,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28792Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28792Y\"></sup> and they have devoted themselves to the service<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28792Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28792Z\"></sup> of the Lord’s people.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28792AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28792AA\"></sup> I urge you, brothers and sisters,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>to submit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28793AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28793AB\"></sup> to such people and to everyone who joins in the work and labors at it.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I was glad when Stephanas, Fortunatus and Achaicus arrived, because they have supplied what was lacking from you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28794AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28794AC\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For they refreshed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28795AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28795AD\"></sup> my spirit and yours also. Such men deserve recognition.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28795AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28795AE\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The churches in the province of Asia<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28796AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28796AF\"></sup> send you greetings. Aquila and Priscilla<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28796AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28796AG\"></sup> greet you warmly in the Lord, and so does the church that meets at their house.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28796AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28796AH\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>All the brothers and sisters here send you greetings. Greet one another with a holy kiss.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28797AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28797AI\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I, Paul, write this greeting in my own hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28798AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28798AJ\"></sup>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>If anyone does not love the Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28799AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28799AK\"></sup> let that person be cursed!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28799AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28799AL\"></sup> Come, Lord!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28799AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28799AM\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>The grace of the Lord Jesus be with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-28800AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-28800AN\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>My love to all of you in Christ Jesus. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;